{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 7,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 330.305,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.508,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I would that you might know",
      "verse": "7:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 2.688,
      "end": 7.239,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that after my father, Lehi, had made an end of prophesying",
      "verse": "7:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 7.419,
      "end": 9.091,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning his seed,",
      "verse": "7:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 9.271,
      "end": 11.639,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "then the Lord spoke to him again, saying",
      "verse": "7:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 11.819,
      "end": 14.141,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it was not meet for him, Lehi,",
      "verse": "7:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 14.321,
      "end": 17.99,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he should take his family into the wilderness alone;",
      "verse": "7:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 18.17,
      "end": 21.374,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but that his sons should take daughters to wife,",
      "verse": "7:1",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 21.554,
      "end": 25.176,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they might raise up seed to the Lord in the land of promise.",
      "verse": "7:1",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 25.856,
      "end": 27.806,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then the Lord commanded him",
      "verse": "7:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 27.986,
      "end": 33.466,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I, Nephi, and my brothers, should again return to the land of Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "7:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 33.646,
      "end": 36.99,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and bring down Ishmael and his family into the wilderness.",
      "verse": "7:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 37.67,
      "end": 40.689,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I, Nephi, did again, with my brothers,",
      "verse": "7:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 40.869,
      "end": 43.934,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "go forth into the wilderness to go up to Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "7:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 44.614,
      "end": 47.308,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then we went up to the house of Ishmael,",
      "verse": "7:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 47.488,
      "end": 50.739,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we gained favor in the sight of Ishmael,",
      "verse": "7:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 50.919,
      "end": 54.17,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so much so that we spoke to him the words of the Lord.",
      "verse": "7:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 54.85,
      "end": 58.472,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then the Lord softened the heart of Ishmael,",
      "verse": "7:5",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 58.652,
      "end": 60.277,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also his household,",
      "verse": "7:5",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 60.457,
      "end": 65.333,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so much so that they took their journey with us down into the wilderness",
      "verse": "7:5",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 65.513,
      "end": 67.138,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to the tent of our father.",
      "verse": "7:5",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 67.818,
      "end": 70.697,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then as we journeyed in the wilderness,",
      "verse": "7:6",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 70.877,
      "end": 72.688,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold Laman and Lemuel,",
      "verse": "7:6",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 72.868,
      "end": 74.958,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and two of the daughters of Ishmael",
      "verse": "7:6",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 75.138,
      "end": 78.342,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the two sons of Ishmael and their families,",
      "verse": "7:6",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 78.522,
      "end": 80.147,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "rebeled against us;",
      "verse": "7:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 80.327,
      "end": 82.742,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, against me, Nephi, and Sam,",
      "verse": "7:6",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 82.922,
      "end": 85.29,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their father, Ishmael, and his wife,",
      "verse": "7:6",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 85.47,
      "end": 87.328,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and his three other daughters.",
      "verse": "7:6",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 88.008,
      "end": 90.469,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then in the which rebellion,",
      "verse": "7:7",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 90.649,
      "end": 94.364,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they were desirous to return to the land of Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "7:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 95.044,
      "end": 98.806,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, being grieved for the hardness of their hearts,",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 98.986,
      "end": 100.983,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "therefore I spoke to them, saying,",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 101.163,
      "end": 103.857,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even to Laman and to Lemuel:",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 104.037,
      "end": 106.034,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold you are my elder brothers,",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 106.214,
      "end": 108.675,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and how is it that you are so hard",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 108.855,
      "end": 111.641,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in your hearts, and so blind in your minds,",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 111.821,
      "end": 114.886,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that you have need that I, your younger brother,",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 115.066,
      "end": 116.506,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should speak to you,",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 116.686,
      "end": 118.962,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, and set an example for you?",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 119.642,
      "end": 123.218,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "How is it that you have not listened to the word of the Lord?",
      "verse": "7:9",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 123.898,
      "end": 126.034,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "How is it that you have forgotten",
      "verse": "7:10",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 126.214,
      "end": 128.35,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that you have seen an angel of the Lord?",
      "verse": "7:10",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 129.03,
      "end": 132.095,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Indeed, and how is it that you have forgotten",
      "verse": "7:11",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 132.275,
      "end": 135.108,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "what great things the Lord has done for us,",
      "verse": "7:11",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 135.288,
      "end": 138.307,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in delivering us out of the hands of Laban,",
      "verse": "7:11",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 138.487,
      "end": 140.67,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also that we should obtain the record?",
      "verse": "7:11",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 141.35,
      "end": 144.415,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Indeed, and how is it that you have forgotten",
      "verse": "7:12",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 144.595,
      "end": 147.335,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord is able to do all things",
      "verse": "7:12",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 147.515,
      "end": 150.673,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to his will, for the children of men,",
      "verse": "7:12",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 150.853,
      "end": 153.547,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if it so be that they exercise faith in him?",
      "verse": "7:12",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 153.727,
      "end": 155.724,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, let us be faithful to him.",
      "verse": "7:12",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 156.404,
      "end": 158.958,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And if it so be that we are faithful to him,",
      "verse": "7:13",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 159.138,
      "end": 161.553,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we shall obtain the land of promise;",
      "verse": "7:13",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 161.733,
      "end": 164.473,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and you shall know at some future period",
      "verse": "7:13",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 164.653,
      "end": 167.3,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the word of the Lord shall be fulfilled",
      "verse": "7:13",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 167.48,
      "end": 169.988,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the destruction of Jerusalem;",
      "verse": "7:13",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 170.168,
      "end": 172.722,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for all things which the Lord has spoken",
      "verse": "7:13",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 172.902,
      "end": 176.292,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the destruction of Jerusalem must be fulfilled.",
      "verse": "7:13",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 176.972,
      "end": 180.78,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, the Spirit of the Lord ceases soon to strive with them;",
      "verse": "7:14",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 180.96,
      "end": 183.561,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold, they have rejected the prophets,",
      "verse": "7:14",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 183.741,
      "end": 186.295,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and Jeremiah have they cast into prison.",
      "verse": "7:14",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 186.475,
      "end": 189.261,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they have sought to take away the life of my father,",
      "verse": "7:14",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 189.441,
      "end": 193.063,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so much so that they have driven him out of the land.",
      "verse": "7:14",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 193.743,
      "end": 195.368,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now behold, I say to you",
      "verse": "7:15",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 195.548,
      "end": 197.916,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that if you will return to Jerusalem",
      "verse": "7:15",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 198.096,
      "end": 200.232,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "you shall also perish with them.",
      "verse": "7:15",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 200.412,
      "end": 203.709,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, if you have choice, go up to the land,",
      "verse": "7:15",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 203.889,
      "end": 206.722,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and remember the words which I speak to you",
      "verse": "7:15",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 206.902,
      "end": 209.317,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that if you go you will also perish;",
      "verse": "7:15",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 209.497,
      "end": 213.166,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for thus the Spirit of the Lord compels me that I should speak.",
      "verse": "7:15",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 213.846,
      "end": 217.329,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then when I, Nephi, had spoken these words to my brothers,",
      "verse": "7:16",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 217.509,
      "end": 218.856,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they were angry with me.",
      "verse": "7:16",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 219.036,
      "end": 221.312,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then they laid their hands upon me,",
      "verse": "7:16",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 221.492,
      "end": 223.582,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold, they were very angry,",
      "verse": "7:16",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 223.762,
      "end": 225.62,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they bound me with cords,",
      "verse": "7:16",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 225.8,
      "end": 228.308,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they sought to take away my life,",
      "verse": "7:16",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 228.488,
      "end": 231.507,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they might leave me in the wilderness",
      "verse": "7:16",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 231.687,
      "end": 233.963,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to be devoured by wild beasts.",
      "verse": "7:16",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 234.643,
      "end": 236.64,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But then I prayed to the Lord, saying:",
      "verse": "7:17",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 236.82,
      "end": 237.795,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O Lord,",
      "verse": "7:17",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 237.975,
      "end": 240.297,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to my faith which is in you,",
      "verse": "7:17",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 240.477,
      "end": 243.774,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "will you deliver me from the hands of my brothers;",
      "verse": "7:17",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 243.954,
      "end": 246.276,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even give me strength",
      "verse": "7:17",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 246.456,
      "end": 249.567,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I may burst these bands with which I am bound.",
      "verse": "7:17",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 250.247,
      "end": 252.569,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then when I had said these words,",
      "verse": "7:18",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 252.749,
      "end": 255.953,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, the bands were loosed from off my hands and feet,",
      "verse": "7:18",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 256.133,
      "end": 258.176,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I stood before my brothers,",
      "verse": "7:18",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 258.356,
      "end": 259.935,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I spoke to them again.",
      "verse": "7:18",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 260.615,
      "end": 262.612,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then they were angry with me again,",
      "verse": "7:19",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 262.792,
      "end": 265.068,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and sought to lay hands upon me;",
      "verse": "7:19",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 265.248,
      "end": 268.22,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but behold, one of the daughters of Ishmael,",
      "verse": "7:19",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 268.4,
      "end": 270.258,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, and also her mother,",
      "verse": "7:19",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 270.438,
      "end": 272.621,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and one of the sons of Ishmael,",
      "verse": "7:19",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 272.801,
      "end": 274.473,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "pleaded with my brothers,",
      "verse": "7:19",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 274.653,
      "end": 277.532,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so much so that they softened their hearts;",
      "verse": "7:19",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 277.712,
      "end": 280.638,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they ceased striving to take away my life.",
      "verse": "7:19",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 281.318,
      "end": 283.361,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then they were sorrowful,",
      "verse": "7:20",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 283.541,
      "end": 285.584,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of their wickedness,",
      "verse": "7:20",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 285.764,
      "end": 288.783,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so much so that they bowed down before me,",
      "verse": "7:20",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 288.963,
      "end": 290.542,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and pleaded with me",
      "verse": "7:20",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 290.722,
      "end": 294.855,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I would forgive them of the thing that they had done against me.",
      "verse": "7:20",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 295.535,
      "end": 299.39,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I did frankly forgive them all that they had done,",
      "verse": "7:21",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 299.57,
      "end": 301.753,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I urged them that they would pray",
      "verse": "7:21",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 301.933,
      "end": 304.209,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to the Lord their God for forgiveness.",
      "verse": "7:21",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 304.389,
      "end": 305.736,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then they did so.",
      "verse": "7:21",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 305.916,
      "end": 308.563,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after they had done praying to the Lord",
      "verse": "7:21",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 308.743,
      "end": 311.204,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we did again travel on our journey",
      "verse": "7:21",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 311.384,
      "end": 313.613,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "towards the tent of our father.",
      "verse": "7:21",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
